    Some complaints

    The refrigerator works fine, and looks great. There are some features that aren't great:
    -The Ice/water dispenser is poorly designed. When you hold a glass under the dispenser and press the glass against the back turn on switch, the ice goes all over the place, and depending on the circumference of the glass, the water more often then not misses the glass. To compensate for this I place my glass carefully under the dispenser and use my other hand to press the turn on switch behind it. A pain. It would have been better to have the control in front where the buttons are.
    -there is no egg holder
    -there is no butter compartment in the door
    -the shelves are not adjustable in the refrigerator side
    -I'd rather have more shelves and not have two drawers on the refrigerator side
